comment: /**  * Returns the method (GET, POST, etc) of the request.  * @return the method  */
code: /**  * Returns the method (GET, POST, etc) of the request.  * @return the method  */ String getMethod().

comment: /**  * Returns the URI of the request.  * @return the URI  */
code: /**  * Returns the URI of the request.  * @return the URI  */ URI getUri().

comment: /**  * Returns a modifiable copy of the headers of the request.  * @return the headers  */
code: /**  * Returns a modifiable copy of the headers of the request.  * @return the headers  */ Map<String, List<String>> getHeaders().

comment: /**  * Returns the remote address from which the request was sent, if available.  * @return the remote address or {@code null}  */
code: /**  * Returns the remote address from which the request was sent, if available.  * @return the remote address or {@code null}  */ String getRemoteAddress().
